}}{{TIDTOC|switch}} ==Overview== "8GS1005DR2E1G", two checkboxes w/ "DGS-1005D" and "DGS-2205" (checked) and a date code of ''0918'' is silkscreened on one particular DGS-2205 B2's board.
The main switch IC is covered w/ a somewhat large (and well attached) heatsink. :The board identifier does not differ significantly from the B2 revision, and, expectedly, the same switch IC is under the heatsink.
